1. Introduction
    This program helps you to configure your vim editor, in order to having a good using experience.
    
2. Directory layout
    ./script : vim script file (.vimrc)
    readme : this file
    
3. Usage
    copy file ".vimrc" in ./script directory to your ./home directory
    follow the instruction of this website : https://blog.csdn.net/xzli8_geo/article/details/78779991
